            "title": "粉錦公路4狗疑遭毒害 3慘死1吐白泡 愛協檢走警追查狂徒",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"粉錦公路發生懷疑毒品案，釀3死 1受傷，警方到場調查事件。黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ace4af20c5e2e3deb42bddf8684f8724/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250206/_2025020604330622320.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">粉錦公路發生懷疑毒品案，釀3死 1受傷，警方到場調查事件。黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>上水發生懷疑毒狗案。今日（6日）凌晨1時許，警方接獲一名女子報案，指在粉錦公路近蓮塘尾榮昌茶座附近，發現3隻狗隻屍體及1隻狗隻口吐白沫，懷疑狗隻遭人落毒。警方接報到場，將案列「殘酷動物」案調查。\n\n</p><h2>3狗死亡 1狗口吐白沫</h2>\n<p>警員接報到場，在一個倉庫的工字鐵下，現場發現3隻兩個多月大的狗BB的屍體，另外一隻狗BB口吐白沫。警方隨後通知愛護動物協會人員，將狗隻屍體及受傷的狗隻協走。\n\n</p>\n<p>據毛守救援義工Ken表示，早前收到熱心市民報料，指在榮昌茶座附近有兩隻狗隻四肢殘缺，其中一隻失去左前肢，另一隻失去左後腳。兩隻狗的傷口齊整，仍然滴血，懷疑被捕獸器弄斷。義工收悉事件後，推測狗隻來自附近一個倉庫。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062112/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"愛護動物協會協走受傷的狗隻作進一步檢查。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eff6f9d92e13aac414ba853eb0882078/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-06-03-08-02_013.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        愛護動物協會協走受傷的狗隻作進一步檢查。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062113/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"3隻狗隻疑遭毒毒死亡。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e3e9fa4f2ecc0da06b79eba9ea198a06/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-06-04-08-49_001.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        3隻狗隻疑遭毒毒死亡。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062114/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一隻狗BB 口吐白沫，由愛協人員帶走檢驗。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b1e022bd7f91b794023b2b48ba6d9922/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-06-04-09-01_006.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一隻狗BB 口吐白沫，由愛協人員帶走檢驗。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062115/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a327f536781b75f1370c438335f45317/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-06-04-08-58_005.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062116/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場亦一個狗隻頭顱骨。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/427b3ad02418c3fadd9a15858dec95c6/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-06-03-07-56_011.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場亦一個狗隻頭顱骨。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062117/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a932f3a662f7f6992310ffca86f56c0a/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-06-03-07-41_006.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>在年初二，Ken及十多名義工成功將兩隻因捕器而腳部受傷的狗隻救出，期間發現附近亦有多隻狗受傷及7隻狗BB，但當時未有將狗BB帶走。義工Ken指該批狗BB 每日都會離開倉庫玩耍，有義工會前來餵飼他們。但前晚收到消息，指最近狗BB不見了，覺得有可疑。有村民今日協助尋找狗BB，發現一隻狗BB伏屍地上。\n\n</p>\n<p>Ken周三晚上前來打算檢走時，仍沒有發現另外6隻，覺得可疑之下，遂四出查看。期間發現多兩隻狗的屍體。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062118/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"義工Ken稱，早前救走兩隻受傷的狗隻。毛守救援提供圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a58662554aec248164bdf541c833b0eb/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_18_50_59_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        義工Ken稱，早前救走兩隻受傷的狗隻。毛守救援提供圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062119/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"狗BB離開倉庫玩耍。毛守救援提供圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0cddafc89399d5bb12baa222abba9db/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_18_51_30.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        狗BB離開倉庫玩耍。毛守救援提供圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062120/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"義工Ken稱，早前救走兩隻受傷的狗隻。毛守救援提供圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6be237ee4d31f5c8089120a57d8caad7/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_18_55_39.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        義工Ken稱，早前救走兩隻受傷的狗隻。毛守救援提供圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062121/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"3隻狗隻疑被毒毒，隨後被放入黑色膠袋中。毛守救援提供圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f974de2bf1e52faf7b082e19ff0b3cb5/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_18_51_27_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        3隻狗隻疑被毒毒，隨後被放入黑色膠袋中。毛守救援提供圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062122/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"7隻狗BB其中3隻疑遭毒害死亡。毛守救援提供圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7e29e03bea2f28c710e78ae1b371f669/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_18_51_29.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        7隻狗BB其中3隻疑遭毒害死亡。毛守救援提供圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>民建聯區議員劉鎮海表示，3隻死亡的狗隻身上有中毒的跡象，包括口吐白沫及嘔吐跡象。雖然未能確定是否中毒，但3隻狗死亡，有合理懷疑被牠們被毒害。現時仍有3隻未找到，估計他們都是「凶多吉少」。他指，新界區最近接連多宗毒狗，懷疑今次的事件與早前的毒狗案有關。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2051087/即時-港聞-粉錦公路4狗疑遭毒害-3慘死1吐白泡-愛協檢走警追查狂徒",
